review:
This has to be one of the prettiest horror games I have ever played.

❌ - There are some technical issues here and there: huge lag spikes, some crashes, etc.

✔️ - The atmosphere was so thick, You can barely breathe;
✔️ - The presentation and graphics put some AAA games to shame;
✔️ - Good scares, and interesting monster;
✔️ - Great game for pretty screenshots;
✔️ - Easy 100% (~5h).

This is a disgustingly underrated hidden gem every horror fan should check out.
With a better story, it could have been on par with [b]Amnesia: The Dark Descent[/b].
